Previously in Elves Must Live 1 if you have not play the first opus of the saga:
The orcs broke the peace treaty they had with the peacful elves civilization. The attack was brutal and gave no chance to the unexperimented elve army. Fortunatly, a young officer managed to organized a safe path to the moutain and saved the elvish survivors. In a last battle, the elves managed to defeat the orc army at the feets of the Ancestral Bastion.

Currently, the princess of the elves got captured by the barbarish orcs and it is up to you to save her from her terible fate. You will have to sneak across the orcs lines and manage to overpass the obstables that will rise on your quests !
